      "type": "text",
      "text": "This spell allows you to place simple, floating light sources on the block you're looking at.$(br2)Modifiers allow you to choose the colour, cause them to decay over time, be placed at your location, or consume all nearby lights.$(br2)$(warning) Lights consumed with $(modifier:deluminator)$() cannot be restored without re-placing them."
